Depends:default-jre, libunixsocket-java, ${misc:Depends}
Description:  an unofficial daemon that facilitates communication with the Signal messaging app.
 signald is a daemon to facilitate communicating with users of the Signal messaging app. It is an
 unofficial signal client and is not in any way endorsed or even approved by Signal Messenger
